Megatron walked throught the hall way, then arrived at the elivator.
"Right now we are on the bridge, this elevator leads us to the engine
room, to a docking tower over top, the throne room, the repair romms and
the quarters." he said, as the door opened up, he stepped in, then
waited for the others to enter. "It is not very impressive yet, but when
I am done, it will be magnificent." he said, putting his hands out over
his head.
